headline: Raymond James CIO Adam Expects 5%-10% Pullback in Stocks
summary: Raymond James CIO Larry Adam says he is cautious going into the end of the year and expects a consolidation in US stocks. Speaking on "Bloomberg Open Interest," Adam adds that he expects stocks to fall 5%-10% which will provide a buying opportunity.
